sql:
SELECT title
FROM books
WHERE book_id IN (SELECT DISTINCT book_id FROM reviews);

SELECT title
FROM books
WHERE book_id IN (SELECT book_id FROM book_publishers WHERE publisher_id = 1);

external_knowledge:
- Top books imply the highest rated and most reviewed; 
- More than 50 reviews mean books with a review count greater than 50; 
- Favored by the most customers imply the books with the highest count of matching customers, where a matching customer is one who prefers the book's genre.
